/>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"喂屌你人地政府官方用優化二字取代加強/改善<br />\n俾埋Link你你都當睇唔到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"397914eae01bf89cd648364f9d72076cade12486","tid":2113021,"uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"你睇返片<br />\n台灣係講&quot;最佳化&quot;<br />\n如果你係用呢個case<br />\n建議你唔好用優化呢個字<br />\n因為優化呢個字真係大陸傳入<br />\n我最先見呢個字係大約2005年<br />\n係D濕鳩中學既型banner寫住&quot;優化教育&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">政府教育好撚鐘意用優化呢個詞<br />\ne.g.&quot;優化學校投訴管理計劃&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/sch-admin/admin/pilot-scheme/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fsch-admin%2Fadmin%2Fpilot-scheme%2Findex.html&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTibHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=08ca0e28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/sch-admin/admin/pilot-scheme/index.html</a><br />\n你自己係政府網睇下呢個字<br />\n你再轉返去英文版<br />\n屌你老母英文都唔會係呢度用optimize, 但中文就不停講乜鳩優化<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係想講電腦既野<br />\n建議你用&quot;效能&quot;<br />\nnvidia優化做得好過amd <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\namd&quot;<span class=\"red\">效能&quot;</span>做得好過intel <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講 隻game優化做得好差<br />\n講 隻game <strong><span class=\"red\">&quot;效能方面寫得好差&quot;</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一樣意思<br />\n中文一直都唔係英文直譯<br />\n表達有好多種方法<br />\n但中國就係多文盲<br />\n所以中國呢幾十年不停造新既歐化詞 以為可以同外國文化接軌<br />\n但同時都係破壞緊中國文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}